                            <comment id="17512712" author="davsclaus" created="Sat, 26 Mar 2022 10:32:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Its bad practice IMHO to have remote XSD imports as that makes your app depedent on that remote service being online.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17513223" author="federico mariani" created="Mon, 28 Mar 2022 08:09:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m sorry I lost your comment, I agree with you, remote XSD import is not a good practice, but XSDs like &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.w3.org/2012/04/XMLSchema.xsd&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://www.w3.org/2012/04/XMLSchema.xsd&lt;/a&gt; use this feature, therefore I opened the PR.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
